1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:04,880
(He says he'll turn me into a prince,
but what's this guy's angle?)

2
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:06,420
Sit down.

3
00:00:11,050 --> 00:00:14,060
Uh, hey... what are you doing?

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:15,970
Didn't I say I was going to make you a prince?

5
00:00:15,970 --> 00:00:18,730
If I go along with this,
will you keep it a secret that I got dumped?

6
00:00:18,730 --> 00:00:21,440
(Looks like I'm not really
in a position to refuse.)

7
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:25,570
I see.
I was wondering why you were suddenly so cooperative.

8
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:29,240
Play along,
and I'll keep your secret.

9
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:31,160
I'll do it! I'll do anything!

10
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,370
I wasn't going to tell anyone anyway,
but whatever.

11
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:34,490
That's a relief...

12
00:00:36,370 --> 00:00:37,660
(He's so close...)

13
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:40,540
(Come to think of it, his eyelashes are really long...)

14
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,130
What? I can't see! Give them back!

15
00:00:44,130 --> 00:00:46,380
Nope.
I'm about to do your makeup.

16
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:48,050
Makeup...?

17
00:00:48,050 --> 00:00:50,630
The school festival is one month from now.

18
00:00:50,630 --> 00:00:53,640
By then, you'll be a prince,
and you'll show that girl what she's missing.

19
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:56,510
Sounds like
I'm the only one getting anything out of this.

20
00:00:56,510 --> 00:00:58,930
Because I happen to be looking for
a makeup model.

21
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:00,520
It's a win-win, isn't it?

22
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:03,650
A model...?
Wouldn't it be easier to just practice on yourself?

23
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:05,940
It's not practice unless you do it on someone else.

24
00:01:05,940 --> 00:01:09,280
Practice? But I'm so plain-looking.

25
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:13,450
You have great features.

26
00:01:13,450 --> 00:01:15,120
Have a little more confidence.

27
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,910
First...

28
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:22,330
Close your eyes.
